---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Building Trust as a CAM — Free Course | Alloy Growth Partners"
  description="A free 6-lesson micro-course for community association managers on building trust with boards, residents, and prospects. From Alloy Growth Partners."
  pageId="resources"
>
<div class="course-page">




<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="crumbs">
          <a href="/courses">Courses</a>
          <span class="sep">/</span>
          <span class="here">Building Trust</span>
        </div>

        <div class="pill-row">
          <span class="pill">Building Trust</span>
          <span class="pill level">Foundations</span>
        </div>

        <h1>Trust-Building for CAM Firms: <em>Reviews, testimonials &amp; case studies.</em></h1>

        <p class="hero-sub">
          Three trust signals decide whether boards consider you or choose you. This course shows you what each one is, where it shows up in the HOA decision process, and how to put the right proof in front of the right board at the right time.
        </p>

        <div class="meta-strip">
          <div class="meta-item">
            <span class="meta-label">Lessons</span>
            <span class="meta-value">10</span>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <span class="meta-label">Quiz</span>
            <span class="meta-value">1</span>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <span class="meta-label">Time</span>
            <span class="meta-value">~60 min</span>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <span class="meta-label">Level</span>
            <span class="meta-value">Foundations</span>
          </div>
          <div class="meta-item">
            <span class="meta-label">Format</span>
            <span class="meta-value">Self-paced</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Enrollment card -->
      <aside class="enroll-card">
        <div class="enroll-card-eyebrow">Free • Open registration</div>
        <div class="enroll-card-price">$0</div>
        <div class="enroll-card-price-note">No card. No upsell. Just the course.</div>

        <a href="/courses/trust-building/lesson" class="btn btn-primary">Start the course →</a>

        <ul class="enroll-includes">
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#d9356e" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
            10 short, focused lessons
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#d9356e" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
            1 knowledge-check quiz
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#d9356e" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
            Built around HOA board decisions
          </li>
          <li>
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#d9356e" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg>
            No prerequisites
          </li>
        </ul>

        <a href="#curriculum" class="btn btn-ghost">↓ Preview the curriculum</a>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHY THIS COURSE -->
<section class="block">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="why-grid">
      <div>
        <div class="section-eyebrow">Why this course</div>
        <div class="why-quote">Trust is the difference between being considered and being chosen.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="why-body">
        <p>HOA boards make high-stakes decisions that affect their communities' finances, property values, and quality of life. Before they award a contract, they're looking for proof you'll deliver — and most CAM firms are showing the wrong proof at the wrong moment.</p>
        <p>Reviews, testimonials, and case studies aren't interchangeable. Each one carries weight at a different stage of the board's journey. By the end of this course, you'll know which signal to use when — and how to make sure the right one is sitting in front of the right board at the right time.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT YOU'LL LEARN -->
<section class="block alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">What you'll learn</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">By the end, you'll be able to —</h2>
    <p class="section-lead">Five concrete capabilities you'll walk away with. Each one ties directly to how boards evaluate firms.</p>

    <div class="objectives">
      <div class="objective">
        <div class="objective-num">1</div>
        <div class="objective-text">Define what trust signals are and explain their importance in CAM marketing.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="objective">
        <div class="objective-num">2</div>
        <div class="objective-text">Differentiate between reviews, testimonials, and case studies — and the role each plays.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="objective">
        <div class="objective-num">3</div>
        <div class="objective-text">Explain why each trust signal matters to HOA boards in their decision-making process.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="objective">
        <div class="objective-num">4</div>
        <div class="objective-text">Evaluate how different trust signals support various stages of the board journey.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="objective">
        <div class="objective-num">5</div>
        <div class="objective-text">Recognize how showcasing trust signals strengthens credibility and board confidence.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CURRICULUM -->
<section class="block" id="curriculum">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">Course curriculum</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Five modules. Ten lessons. One quiz.</h2>
    <p class="section-lead">Each module unpacks one trust signal — what it is, why it matters, and the extra factors that change its impact.</p>

    <div class="curriculum">

      <!-- MODULE 0 — Introduction -->
      <div class="module">
        <div class="module-head">
          <div class="module-mark intro">01</div>
          <div class="module-info">
            <span class="module-tag">Module 1 · Introduction</span>
            <span class="module-title">Why trust signals matter to HOA boards</span>
          </div>
          <div class="module-meta">2 lessons</div>
        </div>
        <div class="module-body">
          <a class="lesson" href="#">
            <span class="lesson-num">01</span>
            <span class="lesson-title">Intro to <em>Trust-Building for CAM Firms</em></span>
            <span class="lesson-type"><span class="dot"></span>Lesson · 4 min</span>
          </a>
          <a class="lesson" href="#">
            <span class="lesson-num">02</span>
            <span class="lesson-title">Why trust signals matter to HOA boards</span>
            <span class="lesson-type"><span class="dot"></span>Lesson · 6 min</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- MODULE 1 — Reviews -->
      <div class="module">
        <div class="module-head">
          <div class="module-mark reviews">02</div>
          <div class="module-info">
            <span class="module-tag">Module 2 · Reviews</span>
            <span class="module-title">Homeowner voices, board decisions</span>
          </div>
          <div class="module-meta">2 lessons</div>
        </div>
        <div class="module-body">
          <a class="lesson" href="#">
            <span class="lesson-num">03</span>
            <span class="lesson-title">What reviews are and why they carry weight</span>
            <span class="lesson-type"><span class="dot"></span>Lesson · 7 min</span>
          </a>
          <a class="lesson" href="#">
            <span class="lesson-num">04</span>
            <span class="lesson-title">Reviews: extra factors that influence impact</span>
            <span class="lesson-type"><span class="dot"></span>Lesson · 5 min</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- MODULE 2 — Testimonials -->
      <div class="module">
        <div class="module-head">
          <div class="module-mark testimonials">03</div>
          <div class="module-info">
            <span class="module-tag">Module 3 · Testimonials</span>
            <span class="module-title">Personal stories that reassure</span>
          </div>
          <div class="module-meta">2 lessons</div>
        </div>
        <div class="module-body">
          <a class="lesson" href="#">
            <span class="lesson-num">05</span>
            <span class="lesson-title">What testimonials are and why they stand out</span>
            <span class="lesson-type"><span class="dot"></span>Lesson · 6 min</span>
          </a>
          <a class="lesson" href="#">
            <span class="lesson-num">06</span>
            <span class="lesson-title">Testimonials: extra factors that influence impact</span>
            <span class="lesson-type"><span class="dot"></span>Lesson · 5 min</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- MODULE 3 — Case Studies -->
      <div class="module">
        <div class="module-head">
          <div class="module-mark cases">04</div>
          <div class="module-info">
            <span class="module-tag">Module 4 · Case studies</span>
            <span class="module-title">Proof boards can see in action</span>
          </div>
          <div class="module-meta">2 lessons</div>
        </div>
        <div class="module-body">
          <a class="lesson" href="#">
            <span class="lesson-num">07</span>
            <span class="lesson-title">What case studies are and why they convince</span>
            <span class="lesson-type"><span class="dot"></span>Lesson · 7 min</span>
          </a>
          <a class="lesson" href="#">
            <span class="lesson-num">08</span>
            <span class="lesson-title">Case studies: extra factors that influence impact</span>
            <span class="lesson-type"><span class="dot"></span>Lesson · 6 min</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- MODULE 4 — Conclusion -->
      <div class="module">
        <div class="module-head">
          <div class="module-mark conclusion">05</div>
          <div class="module-info">
            <span class="module-tag">Module 5 · Wrap-up</span>
            <span class="module-title">From proof to persuasion</span>
          </div>
          <div class="module-meta">2 lessons + quiz</div>
        </div>
        <div class="module-body">
          <a class="lesson" href="#">
            <span class="lesson-num">09</span>
            <span class="lesson-title">Recapping the 3 trust signals</span>
            <span class="lesson-type"><span class="dot"></span>Lesson · 4 min</span>
          </a>
          <a class="lesson" href="#">
            <span class="lesson-num">10</span>
            <span class="lesson-title">From proof to persuasion: using trust signals effectively</span>
            <span class="lesson-type"><span class="dot"></span>Lesson · 6 min</span>
          </a>
          <a class="lesson quiz" href="/courses/trust-building/quiz">
            <span class="lesson-num">★</span>
            <span class="lesson-title">Check your learning — Trust-Building knowledge check</span>
            <span class="lesson-type"><span class="dot"></span>Quiz · 5 min</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FINAL CTA -->
<section class="final-cta" id="start">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <div class="final-cta-eyebrow">Ready to start?</div>
    <h2>Show the right proof at the right moment.</h2>
    <p>10 lessons. ~60 minutes. No card, no upsell. Just the framework — and a knowledge check at the end.</p>
    <div class="final-cta-actions">
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary-on-dark">Start the course →</a>
      <a href="/courses" class="btn btn-secondary-on-dark">Browse all courses</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
/* ---------- Page reset / base ---------- */
.container {
    max-width: 1180px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 40px;
  }
  .container-narrow {
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 40px;
  }

  /* ---------- Top bar (minimal — just to anchor the page) ---------- */
  .topbar {
    background: #fff;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    padding: 18px 0;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 50;
  }
  .topbar-inner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }
  .topbar-brand {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--alloy-purple);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .topbar-brand .dot { color: var(--alloy-pink); }
  .topbar-back {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--alloy-purple);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .topbar-back:hover { color: var(--alloy-pink); }

  /* ---------- Hero ---------- */
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #fbf8f3 0%, #fff 100%);
    padding: 72px 0 64px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -160px;
    right: -120px;
    width: 460px;
    height: 460px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(245,216,128,0.35) 0%, transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.4fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: start;
    position: relative;
  }
  .crumbs {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .crumbs .sep { color: #d0c8db; }
  .crumbs a { color: var(--fg-muted); }
  .crumbs a:hover { color: var(--alloy-pink); }
  .crumbs .here { color: var(--alloy-purple); }

  .pill-row {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    background: rgba(217,53,110,0.10);
    color: var(--alloy-pink);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    border-radius: 999px;
  }
  .pill.level {
    background: rgba(174,215,208,0.30);
    color: #2d6c63;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(36px, 4.6vw, 56px);
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--alloy-purple);
    margin: 0 0 22px;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }
  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: normal;
    color: var(--alloy-pink);
  }
  .hero-sub {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #555;
    max-width: 560px;
    margin: 0 0 32px;
  }

  /* meta strip — under hero copy */
  .meta-strip {
    display: flex;
    gap: 28px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding: 18px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .meta-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }
  .meta-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
  }
  .meta-value {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--alloy-purple);
  }

  /* ---------- Hero enrollment card ---------- */
  .enroll-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 28px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .enroll-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg,
      var(--alloy-pink) 0%, var(--alloy-pink) 33%,
      var(--alloy-yellow) 33%, var(--alloy-yellow) 66%,
      var(--alloy-green) 66%, var(--alloy-green) 100%);
  }
  .enroll-card-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--alloy-pink);
    margin: 6px 0 14px;
  }
  .enroll-card-price {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 36px;
    color: var(--alloy-purple);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .enroll-card-price-note {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #888;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }
  .enroll-includes {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    padding-top: 18px;
  }
  .enroll-includes li {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--alloy-purple);
  }
  .enroll-includes svg {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.10em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 14px 22px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.18s var(--ease-standard);
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--alloy-pink);
    color: #fff;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--alloy-pink-hover); color: #fff; transform: translateY(-1px); box-shadow: var(--shadow-pink); }
  .btn-ghost {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--alloy-purple);
    padding: 8px 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover { color: var(--alloy-pink); }

  /* ---------- Section base ---------- */
  section.block { padding: 80px 0; }
  section.block.alt { background: var(--alloy-off-white); }

  .section-eyebrow {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--alloy-pink);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3.2vw, 40px);
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    color: var(--alloy-purple);
    margin: 0 0 18px;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
  .section-lead {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #555;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 0 40px;
  }

  /* ---------- Why this course ---------- */
  .why-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1.3fr);
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: start;
  }
  .why-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 28px;
    line-height: 1.25;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--alloy-purple);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--alloy-pink);
    padding-left: 22px;
  }
  .why-body {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: #444;
  }
  .why-body p { margin: 0 0 18px; }
  .why-body p:last-child { margin: 0; }

  /* ---------- What you'll learn ---------- */
  .objectives {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 18px;
  }
  .objective {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 22px 24px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    transition: all 0.18s var(--ease-standard);
  }
  .objective:hover {
    border-color: var(--alloy-pink);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }
  .objective-num {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--alloy-purple);
    color: #fff;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 14px;
  }
  .objective-text {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: var(--alloy-purple);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ---------- Curriculum ---------- */
  .curriculum {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  .module {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 14px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: box-shadow 0.18s var(--ease-standard);
  }
  .module:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm); }

  .module-head {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: auto 1fr auto;
    gap: 18px;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 22px 26px;
    cursor: pointer;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .module-mark {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--alloy-purple);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .module-mark.intro { background: rgba(56,28,79,0.08); color: var(--alloy-purple); }
  .module-mark.reviews { background: var(--alloy-pink-tint); color: var(--alloy-pink); }
  .module-mark.testimonials { background: var(--alloy-yellow-tint); color: #b08a1a; }
  .module-mark.cases { background: var(--alloy-green-tint); color: #2d6c63; }
  .module-mark.conclusion { background: rgba(56,28,79,0.08); color: var(--alloy-purple); }

  .module-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; min-width: 0; }
  .module-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
  }
  .module-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 19px;
    color: var(--alloy-purple);
    line-height: 1.3;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .module-meta {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--fg-muted);
    flex-shrink: 0;
